{"type": "article", "id": 8005, "title": "Modern Times 皮革托盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-01T07:23:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234618h0nuoysgqc8vBeFK.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t香港生活概念店舖 Modern Times 店内摆设了一个皮革制的托盘，没想到却频频被人问起是否可以出售，所以设计师 Roberu 将它作为一个特别系列产品推出了。这款托盘有棕色，红色和黑色可选，材料是精致的皮革，底部配有一块幼细毛布使得底盘更加稳定，看上去优雅美丽。目前售价为 680 港币，<a href=\"http://www.moderntimes.hk/#!roberu-for-modern-times-series/chzh\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346169LUqlWkFpwVsh5aG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234616kT5VbUpcSNzZfu4y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.00257732\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234617yPXh31OJd6nfZUcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.97953964\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234617lkbUq0m3aw9Bt2ip.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.00515464\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234618OBQYy0gXcnp4IC7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.98976982\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</